      "seed": 528704047,
      "version": 120,
      "versionNonce": 1494507457,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1784365343888,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Databases don't load the whole table,\nUserSession table essentially is the table they are\ndescribing. It's a table dedicated strictly to mapping\na session token to a user and an expiration date.\ninside token_hash I used index=True.\nWith an index, the database uses a highly efficient\nsearch tree (B-Tree) to find the token instantly,\nrather than scanning row by row.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "2YNaYJI4Bqbm6U7cbA6AR",
      "originalText": "Databases don't load the whole table,\nUserSession table essentially is the table they are describing. It's a table dedicated strictly to mapping a session token to a user and an expiration date.\ninside token_hash I used index=True.\nWith an index, the database uses a highly efficient search tree (B-Tree) to find the token instantly, rather than scanning row by row.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
